"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1934521-Paris-Olympics-closing-ceremony-start-time-TV-channel\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  The2024 Paris Olympic Gamesdraws to a close today following over two weeks of thrilling sporting action.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 106, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 10, \"end\": 15, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.314159761855166e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A total of 329 medal events have been showcased during the event, which began with a spectacular display along the River Seine featuring athletes from all participating nations.\", \"from\": 107, \"to\": 284, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 222, \"end\": 233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"River Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thomas Jolly, the director of both the opening and closing ceremonies, has dubbed the concluding event 'Records', which will mark the end of a widely celebrated Games.\", \"from\": 286, \"to\": 453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 286, \"end\": 292, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"score\": 0.6603212225016643, \"rank\": 0.33506219374682217, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Tank_Engine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rumours of celebrity guests and an expected fireworks display hint at a grand celebration befitting the 17 days of athletic excellence witnessed in Paris and beyond.\", \"from\": 454, \"to\": 619, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 602, \"end\": 607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.314159761855166e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But when does the closing ceremony actually start?\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And what TV channel will it be show on?\", \"from\": 672, \"to\": 711, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything you need to know:  The closing ceremony is set to begin on Sunday at 8:00pm and is expected to last for two-and-a-half hours, finishing at around 10:30pm.\", \"from\": 712, \"to\": 884, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For those planning to watch the entire show, director Jolly promises a spectacle, with 'world-renowned singers' slated to perform on the massive 2,800 square metre stage.\", \"from\": 885, \"to\": 1055, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Snoop Dogg, who has been seen numerous times throughout the games cheering on Team USA, is rumoured to be among the performers.\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1184, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Snoop Dogg\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Snoop_Dogg\"}, {\"begin\": 1135, \"end\": 1143, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9952111331253308, \"rank\": 0.004802065542212481, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"UK viewers can tune intoBBCOne, BBC iPlayer and the BBC Sport website and app to catch the closing ceremony.\", \"from\": 1186, \"to\": 1294, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1186, \"end\": 1188, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999997697359769, \"rank\": 1.9321428850272698e-07, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9992964243698269, \"rank\": 0.0004573286973666737, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"iPlayer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_iPlayer\"}, {\"begin\": 1238, \"end\": 1247, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\", \"score\": 0.9999832650127848, \"rank\": 9.76874972893428e-06, \"text\": \"BBC Sport\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC_Online\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The BBC's coverage will begin an hour earlier, at 7:00pm, providing ample time to build up to the event and reflect on the achievements of Team GB's competitors.\", \"from\": 1295, \"to\": 1456, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1299, \"end\": 1302, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"score\": 0.9992964243698269, \"rank\": 0.0004573286973666737, \"text\": \"BBC\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/BBC\"}, {\"begin\": 1434, \"end\": 1441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9872788654263922, \"rank\": 0.012882304614995245, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it remains unconfirmed whetherHollywoodA-listerTom Cruisewill take part in the ceremony, rumours are circulating that he might pull off a daring stunt in true Mission: Impossible fashion.\", \"from\": 1460, \"to\": 1653, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The presence of Cruise would symbolically hand over the reins to the United States, the host nation for the 2028 Games in Los Angeles.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1723, \"end\": 1736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999955442444068, \"rank\": 2.376176590961197e-06, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1776, \"end\": 1787, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"score\": 0.999999999994543, \"rank\": 5.515780747614472e-12, \"text\": \"Los Angeles\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Los_Angeles\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the star-studded opening ceremony - which saw performances from Lady Gaga, Celine Dion, and Aya Nakamura - is anything to go by, an appearance from the Top Gun actor would not be particularly surprising.\", \"from\": 1790, \"to\": 1996, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1857, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Lady Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\"}, {\"begin\": 1868, \"end\": 1879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.566599784692572e-35, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony is set to unfold at the Stade de France.\", \"from\": 1998, \"to\": 2059, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2043, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The venue has already seen action during these Games, hosting Rugby sevens matches and record-breaking athletics events, as well as the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 2060, \"to\": 2213, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Highlights at the stadium included Armand 'Mondo' Duplantis' men's pole vault world record, Sydney McLaughlin-Levrone's 400m hurdles world best, and Keely Hodgkinson's 800m victory for Team GB.\", \"from\": 2215, \"to\": 2408, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2307, \"end\": 2313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9996519530241675, \"rank\": 0.0003481070573686156, \"text\": \"Sydney\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sydney\"}, {\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2380, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Keely Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Keely_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9872788654263922, \"rank\": 0.012882304614995245, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2412, \"to\": 2521, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2522, \"to\": 2598, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2599, \"to\": 2631, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  In stark contrast to the rain-soaked opening ceremony along the Seine, Sunday is predicted to be one of the hottest days of the year.\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2789, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2720, \"end\": 2725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999985520844, \"rank\": 1.187838327655099e-09, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"According to weather reports, temperatures are expected to reach 33C in Paris during the ceremony, with the roofless Stade de France exposed to the elements.\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2947, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2862, \"end\": 2867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.314159761855166e-15, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2907, \"end\": 2922, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Thankfully, no rainfall is forecasted for the event.\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 3001, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3003, \"to\": 3172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3140, \"end\": 3153, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6827037604666246e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3174, \"to\": 3241, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3189, \"end\": 3202, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.6827037604666246e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"